	\section{Images in LaTeX}
	LaTeX allows inserting images using the `graphicx` package. Below are two examples:
	
	\begin{figure}[h]
		\centering
		\includegraphics[width=0.6\textwidth]{img1.png}
		\caption{Example Image 1}
		\label{fig:image1}
	\end{figure}
	
	\begin{figure}[h]
		\centering
		\includegraphics[width=0.6\textwidth]{img2.png}
		\caption{Example Image 2}
		\label{fig:image2}
	\end{figure}
	
